</div>
</div>', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">SECTION 1: RENTAL PROPERTY APPLICATION FORM</strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Good morning, McMurray’s Real Estate, Peter speaking. How may I help you?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Hi Peter. My name is Susan. I’m calling from Australia. I’ll be moving to New Zealand soon and I was hoping you could help me find somewhere to live in Auckland.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Would be pleased to. I just need to get some information about what you want so we can find the perfect place.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Sounds good.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Let’s start with some personal details. What’s your last name?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> It’s Smith.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> And your phone number?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> I only have a mobile, is that okay?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> That’s fine.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Okay, it’s <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"18\">(1) 614381997</strong></span>. But if you want to contact me, usually the best way is by email.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> OK, what’s your email address then?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> It’s susansmith@<span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"23\">(2) post.com</strong></span>. Thanks.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Now, you said you’re living in Australia, right? In Brisbane?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> OK. What’s your address in Brisbane then?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> 234 Becketts—that’s B-E-C-K-E-double T-S Road, Brisbane, 4-0-5-4.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Right. Will you be working in New Zealand?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Yes, I have a job at Auckland Hospital.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Oh, are you a nurse?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Most people assume that or think I’m a doctor, but actually I’m a <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"73\">(3) chemist</strong>.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Oh, sorry.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> That’s OK.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> When will you need the accommodation from?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Well, I don’t start work until February 25th, but I’d like to give myself some time to settle in. A couple of weeks would be nice. Let’s say from February 10th.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Our leases start from a Monday, and the Monday closest to that is February 8th. Would that suit?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> That’s fine.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"28\" />\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Okay, let’s talk about what kind of place you’d like to rent.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Hmm, I like the outdoors, so my dream would be a house that has its own <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"79\">(4) garden</strong>.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Is there anything else you’d consider? An apartment, for example?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> I don’t know, they usually don’t have an outdoor area, but I guess as an alternative, if you could find me one with a large <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"131\">(5) balcony</strong></span>, I’d be happy.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> How many rooms do you want?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Usually one-bedroom places are too small. Two would be ideal.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Now, what would you like to have in the place when you move in?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> I’m bringing most of what I need with me. I have beds and sofas and a television, all that sort of stuff, so none of that is necessary.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Sounds like you want a partially furnished house. With a washing machine?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Actually, I’m bringing that too. All I really need in the place is a <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"76\">(6) fridge</strong></span>. I don’t have one, so we’ll definitely need one.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Okay. Can you find something like that for around $350 a week?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Well, I’ll certainly try. I’ll start looking for places that cost around $300 and see if there’s anything suitable. You definitely won’t need to pay more than <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"166\">(7) 400</strong> </span>for something like that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"41\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Oh, that’s good. I couldn’t pay more than that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"42\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Alright, I’ll see what I can find. You’re working at the hospital—do you want to live somewhere near there?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"43\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"43\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> Most people think it’s strange, but I don’t like living close to work. But I’m a mad keen surfer, so it’s important for me to be close to the <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"43\" data-index-in-node=\"149\">(8) beach</strong>.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"44\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"44\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Okay. Do you need to be near public transport?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"45\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"45\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> No, I usually drive to work because I work a lot of shift work. So wherever I live, we’ll need to have <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"45\" data-index-in-node=\"110\">(9) parking</strong></span> close to the door, so I won’t have to walk far at night.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"46\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"46\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Anything else?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"47\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"47\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Susan:</strong> I’ve heard that power bills can get quite expensive, especially in the winter. It would be great if <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"47\" data-index-in-node=\"107\">(10) electricity</strong></span> was part of the rent.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"48\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"48\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> OK, just one last question for our records: where did you hear about us?</p>\n"}]', 0);
